data.description: A coveted location just steps to McEuen Park, Tubbs Hill and downtown Coeur d'Alene, this 3 bed 2 bath, 1,726 sq ft single level home with a finish basement offers tons of potential for your finishing touches. Amenities include gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings in living room, SS appliances, family room, cold cellar on lower level with a fully fenced backyard, stamped concrete patio and sitting area. Watch the downtown fireworks right from the back yard! You cannot beat this location so come check it out.
